videos.headline: Temple converts fake punt for 36-yard TD
videos.description: Temple's Todd Centeio takes the snap and throws to Freddie Johnson to catch Maryland by surprise.

videos.headline: 330-lb lineman trucks his way through for Temple TD
videos.description: Freddy Booth-Lloyd pushes his way through for the Owls TD giving them the lead 14-0.

videos.headline: Yeboah gets wide open for Temple TD
videos.description: Temple Owls QB Anthony Russo lets one fly to WR Kenny Yeboah for a 47-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Bradley intercepts Hill for 78-yd Temple TD
videos.description: Temple linebacker Shaun Bradley reads Maryland QB Kasim Hill perfectly for an 78-yard pick-six.
